Then dips his hand a copious draught to drink‚ One shoulder testing on the mossy brink. ’Twas then his beauty fired the nymphs at play To leave the dance they love, and haste away;

A little splash-and all around is still. Afar Alcides calls, his love to save, But nought save Echo answers from the wave.
